data.description: ***Assumable FHA loan of $244k at 2.25% or Seller Credit of $9,000 to go towards 2-1 Rate buy down, closing costs, or Prepaids*** Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Riverview, Florida, where luxury and comfort unite in perfect harmony! This stunning 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence boasts a highly sought-after floorplan that offers a lifestyle of both elegance and functionality. As you step inside, you'll be captivated by the OPEN LIVING SPACES both downstairs and upstairs. Every room is designed for both beauty and practicality. The kitchen is a chef's delight with an island for all your culinary adventures. The GENEROUS MASTER SUITE located on the main level is a haven of relaxation, with a walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom and dual sinks. It's the perfect retreat after a long day. FOUR ADDITIONAL BEDROOMS which can be found upstairs ensure there's ample space for family and guests. Each bedroom offers comfort and style, with plenty of natural light. Step outside to your private backyard, where you'll find an added concrete pad for OUTDOOR LIVING. Of course you're located in a great community offering amenities like a swimming pool, playground, and more, providing endless options for RELAXATION AND RECREATION. Riverview is known for its proximity to great schools, shopping, dining, and all that the Tampa Bay area has to offer. You'll be just a short drive from the I-75 making commuting a breeze. This is your opportunity to own a home that beautifully balances elegance with everyday convenience. Don't miss the chance to make this sought-after property your own. Schedule a viewing today and experience the lifestyle you've been dreaming of. Your new beginning starts here.
